trans-unit.source: Specifies the page resolution as a qualitative, non-numerical, value.
trans-unit.target: 指定的頁面解析度為質化、 非數值的值。

trans-unit.source: You can use this type as an alternative, or supplement, to stating resolution in dots per inch (dpi).
trans-unit.target: 您可以使用此類型做為替代方案或補充，指出每英吋點數 (dpi) 中的解析。

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used to provide values for the <xref:System.Printing.PageResolution.QualitativeResolution%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 這個列舉型別用來提供值<xref:System.Printing.PageResolution.QualitativeResolution%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Printing.PageResolution.QualitativeResolution%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PageResolution> class, in turn, is used to provide values for the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A> property where it specifies the various resolutions that a printer supports, and the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageResolution%2A> property, where it instructs a printer what resolution to use.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.PageResolution>類別，接著用來提供值<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>它用來指定各種不同的解析度印表機支援的屬性和<xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageResolution%2A>屬性，其中它會指示印表機来使用何種解析度。</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageResolution%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PageResolution>

trans-unit.source: The default qualitative resolution for the printer.
trans-unit.target: 印表機預設質化解析度。

trans-unit.source: Draft-level quality, which is 300 dpi for most printers.
trans-unit.target: 草稿層級品質，也就是 300 dpi 大部分的印表機。

trans-unit.source: High quality, which is 1200 dpi or greater for most printers.
trans-unit.target: 高品質，也就是 1200 dpi 或更高的大多數的印表機。

trans-unit.source: Normal quality, which is 600 dpi for most printers.
trans-unit.target: 普通品質，也就是 600 dpi，大部分的印表機。

trans-unit.source: The feature (whose options are represented by this enumeration) is set to an option not defined in the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397).
trans-unit.target: 功能 （其選項由這個列舉表示） 設定中未定義的選項為[列印結構描述](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)。
